milestones.description: Bruce Edgar has become the top scorer for NZ in ODIs with 995 runs, going past John Wright's 956
Chris Tavaré and Allan Lamb's 190-run partnership is the highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 159 between David Gower and Allan Lamb
Chris Tavaré and Allan Lamb's 190-run partnership is ENG's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 176 between Fletcher and Dennis Amiss
Chris Tavaré and Allan Lamb's 190-run partnership is ENG's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 159 between David Gower and Allan Lamb
